text: Sånger för december was released on 22 November 2006, and is a Christmas album by Uno Svenningsson and Irma Schultz Keller, with guests. The Christmas songs were newly-written and newly-translated original songs, but no traditional Christmas songs in Sweden. ==Track listing== Names within brackets refer to performer. #Sånger för december - Intro #När julen rullar över världen (Uno Svenningsson) #Jag tror det blir snö i natt (Irma Schultz) #Ängel (Uno Svenningsson & Irma Schultz) #Första snön är alltid vitast (Uno Svenningsson) #Så underbart!
